module: b1-38
level: B1
sequence: 38
slug: complex-sentence-integration
version: '2.0'
title: Інтеграція складних речень
subtitle: Complex Sentence Integration
content_outline:
- section: Тест
  points:
  - Diagnostic quiz on complex sentences — trap students into using simple sentences
    where a complex one is better/needed
  - Self-assessment questions
- section: Пояснення
  points:
  - 'Two-Clause Combinations — focus on «і» vs «а» contrast errors; learner error:
    mixing up additive and contrastive conjunctions'
  - Three+ Clause Sentences — use the 'Rule of Three' from folk tales as a structural
    model
  - 'Coordination + Subordination — State Standard §4.4.3: mastering mixed types (cause,
    condition, purpose) in one sentence'
  - 'Punctuation and Style — The Comma Rule is structural (hard), not breath-based;
    learner error: omitting commas before «що», «який», «коли»; Melodic syntax: rhythm
    in long sentences'
- section: Практика
  points:
  - Build multi-clause sentences — practice sequential and parallel structures
  - Edit for clarity — focus on correcting «що» vs «який» confusion
- section: Діалоги
  points:
  - 'Complex sentences in conversation — distinguish register: «бо» (casual) vs «тому
    що» (formal)'
  - Multi-clause scenarios
vocabulary_hints:
  required:
  - інтеграція (integration)
  - складний (complex)
  - сурядний (coordinating)
  - підрядний (subordinating)
  - багатокомпонентний (multi-component)
  - структура (structure)
  - кома (comma)
  - розділовий знак (punctuation mark)
  - а (and/but) — не ..., а ... (not ..., but ...); а також (and also)
  - але (but) — гарний, але дорогий; хотів, але не зміг
  - щоб (in order to/that) — для того, щоб (in order to); хочу, щоб... (want that...)
  - бо (because) — не прийшов, бо захворів — casual register
  - тому що (because) — тому що це закон — neutral/formal register
  recommended:
  - вкладений (nested)
  - паралельний (parallel)
  - зрозумілість (clarity)
  - стиль (style)
  - хоча (although) — хоча було пізно; хоча він знав
  - якщо (if) — якщо буде час; якщо ти не проти
activity_hints:
- type: error-correction
  focus: Build multi-clause sentences
  items: 25
- type: error-correction
  focus: Fix complex sentence errors
  items: 20
- type: fill-in
  focus: Complete integrated sentences
  items: 15
- type: fill-in
  focus: Write complex paragraphs
  items: 10
focus: grammar
pedagogy: TTT
prerequisites:
- b1-37 (Temporal Clauses)
connects_to:
- b1-39 (Reported Statements)
objectives:
- Learner can combine причинові, часові, умовні clauses
- Learner can build multi-clause sentences
- Learner can choose appropriate connectors for context
- Learner can manage complex sentence structure
grammar:
- Combining multiple clause types
- Coordination and subordination together
- Multi-clause sentence management
register: розмовний
phase: B1.3b [Complex Sentences]
persona:
  voice: Senior Language & Culture Specialist
  role: Novel Editor
word_target: 4000
